      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASCOT SHOWTIME (2) has had a month off and has switched yards since coming from this barrier and getting home by more than 8 metres at Albion Park. Two-time winner at this circuit and distance and looks well placed so can make an immediate impact. The recent form of LACHIES IDEAL (1) may not leap off the page but he has been coming from wider or second row barriers. Looking for big improvement from the ace draw. WHENS LUNCH (4) has won the last two times she has raced here, coming from a similar barrier and digging deep to get home by a neck last start. Could strike again. EBBONY STORM (3) turned in a good effort last start to come from the back row and clock in third at this circuit and distance. Draws for another good showing.",
